Risus Pages - Gone But Not Forgotten

The following is a list of Risus links )from the Cumberland Risus links list and other places) that are no longer online. However, they ARE still accessible thanks to the magic of the Wayback Machine (http://www.archive.org/web/web.php). The links below are linked to the archived versions of these websites. If you find a link that should not be on this list, please let me know via the Risus Talk mailing list on Yahoo Groups (Risustalk-owner at yahoogroups.com).
